-- Swiss Court Upholds Nespresso Rival Ruling, Le Temps Says
-- B y   D e r m o t   D o h e r t y
-- 2011-12-23T08:59:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-23/swiss-court-upholds-nespresso-rival-ruling-le-temps-says.html
A Swiss court based in the canton of
Vaud upheld a ruling preventing the sale of  Ethical Coffee Co. 
capsules that are compatible with Nespresso machines, Le Temps
reported.  Ethical Coffee plans to appeal the decision, the newspaper
reported. The company has sold 300 million capsules this year,
the  newspaper  said, citing Chief Executive Officer Jean-Paul
Gaillard.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dermot Doherty in Zurich at 
 ddoherty9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sara Marley at 
 smarley1@bloomberg.net  